OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781449872
OL,3,CNew sensor could detect arthritis
OL,4,Cbefore major joint damage occurs
OL,6,FThe 14-month project is being led by
OL,7,FProfessor Katherine Staines, with
OL,8,FProfessor Bhavik Patel and Dr Lisa
OL,9,FMullen, all from the University's
OL,10,FCentre for Lifelong Health.
OL,12,FSupported by #107,824 from Arthritis
OL,13,FUK, the research will apply advanced
OL,14,Fsensing technology to osteoarthritis
OL,15,Ffor the first time.
OL,17,FOsteoarthritis affects more than 10
OL,18,Fmillion people across the UK and is
OL,19,Fone of the leading causes of pain,
OL,20,Fstiffness, and reduced mobility.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781449872
OL,3,CNew sensor could detect arthritis
OL,4,Cbefore major joint damage occurs
OL,6,FDespite its widespread impact, the
OL,7,Fcondition is often only diagnosed once
OL,8,Fsignificant damage has already
OL,9,Foccurred inside the joint.
OL,11,FCurrent treatments can help manage
OL,12,Fsymptoms, but there is still no
OL,13,Freliable way to identify who is at
OL,14,Frisk or to detect the disease in its
OL,15,Fearliest stages.
OL,17,FResearchers at Brighton hope to change
OL,18,Fthat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
