PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781449872
OL,3,CNew sensor could detect arthritis
OL,4,Cbefore major joint damage occurs
OL,6,FThat's the natural fluid that cushions
OL,7,Fand lubricates joints to understand
OL,8,Fwhether it can identify a distinct
OL,9,Fbiological pattern linked to
OL,10,Fosteoarthritis.
OL,12,FIf successful, the long-term ambition
OL,13,Fis to develop the technology into a
OL,14,Ftool that could one day support
OL,15,Fearlier diagnosis in clinics and help
OL,16,Fmonitor joint health over time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
